OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784135918
OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FAstronomers have discovered a faint
OL,8,Fnew planet that has been hidden from
OL,9,Fview for more than ten years.
OL,11,FThe planet was seen orbiting a young
OL,12,Fstar called Beta Pictoris, 63 light-
OL,13,Fyears away from Earth.
OL,15,FIt is one of three cold gas planets to
OL,16,Fbe found around the star. However, it
OL,17,Fwas not previously spotted due to
OL,18,Fbeing 100 times fainter than the
OL,19,Fothers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
