FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784135918
OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FUnusually, two teams of scientists,
OL,8,Fone German and Scottish-led, and a
OL,9,FCalifornia team, discovered the planet
OL,10,Fa few days apart, late last year.
OL,12,FIt was only while observing the
OL,13,Fbrighter planets that they caught
OL,14,Fsight of it for the first time.
OL,16,F"It was very much playing hide-and-
OL,17,Fseek for 11 years," said the European
OL,18,FSouthern Observatory's Markus Bonse,
OL,19,Fco-leader of the German and Scottish
OL,20,Fteam who were first to discover the
OL,21,Fplanet.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784135918
OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FA second sighting through NASA's Webb
OL,8,FSpace Telescope, which is the biggest
OL,9,Fand most powerful telescope to ever be
OL,10,Flaunched into space, confirmed the
OL,11,Fplanet's existence.
OL,13,F"We've now built a picture of this
OL,14,Fplanet...and we are very excited to
OL,15,Fsee what more can be learned about
OL,16,Fit," Ben Sutlieff, an astronomer at
OL,17,Fthe University of Edinburgh, said.
OL,19,FTheir findings were published in the
OL,20,FAstrophysical Journal Letters on
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
