PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784135918
OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FSlightly bigger than Jupiter, the new
OL,8,Fplanet takes 91 years to orbit its
OL,9,Fstar.
OL,11,FIt was born into a star system around
OL,12,F20 million years old, a baby compared
OL,13,Fto the Sun's 4.5 billion years.
OL,15,F"Smaller terrestrial planets could
OL,16,Fstill be forming," said astronomer
OL,17,FAidan Gibbs from the University of
OL,18,FCalifornia, San Diego, who led the
OL,19,FCalifornia team that used the NASA
OL,20,Ftelescope.
OL,26,@xD@RO]
