OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FHe said the planet system is "still in
OL,8,Fthe process of stabilising" from
OL,9,Fhurtling asteroids and comets.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FPlanets that orbit around stars
OL,17,Foutside our solar system are called
OL,18,Fexoplanets.
OL,26,@pD@[O]
