OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784135918
OL,3,CScientists discover new planet after
OL,4,Cit spent a decade playing 'hide-and-
OL,5,Cseek'
OL,7,FThere are 6,000 confirmed exoplanets,
OL,8,Fand less than 100 of these have been
OL,9,Fdetected through direct imaging, NASA
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThey are mostly sighted while passing
OL,13,Fin front of their star, making it
OL,14,Fappear dimmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
